title: Carson Wentz to Commanders; FLASHPOINT: Baker Mayfield
itunes:title: Carson Wentz to Commanders; FLASHPOINT: Baker Mayfield
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including Carson Wentz being traded to the Commanders and the Seahawks releasing Bobby Wagner. The Titans sign Harold Landry to a massive deal, and Mitchell Trubisky is... wait WHAT? Browns reporter Tony Grossi stops by for Episode 2 of “FLASHPOINT” to talk about Baker Mayfield’s future in Cleveland.
